---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technology Consulting | Nosyt Labs" description="Strategic technology consulting services. Digital transformation, architecture planning, and technical leadership.">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-surface-primary">
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Technology
          <span class="text-nexus-cyan block">Consulting</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Strategic guidance to navigate complex technology decisions, 
          accelerate digital transformation, and optimize your tech stack.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-nexus-cyan text-deep-space-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-brand-accent-muted transition-colors">
            Book Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/tech-audit" class="border border-nexus-cyan text-nexus-cyan px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-nexus-cyan hover:text-deep-space-black transition-colors">
            Free Tech Audit
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Consulting Services -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface-secondary">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center">
          Consulting <span class="text-nexus-cyan">Expertise</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-primary p-8 rounded-xl border border-surface-tertiary hover:border-nexus-cyan/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-deep-space-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Digital Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Develop comprehensive digital transformation roadmaps aligned with business objectives.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-surface-primary p-8 rounded-xl border border-surface-tertiary hover:border-nexus-cyan/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-deep-space-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Architecture Review</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Evaluate and optimize your technical architecture for scalability and performance.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-surface-primary p-8 rounded-xl border border-surface-tertiary hover:border-nexus-cyan/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-deep-space-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Technology Selection</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Choose the right technologies and frameworks for your specific use cases and goals.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-surface-primary p-8 rounded-xl border border-surface-tertiary hover:border-nexus-cyan/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-deep-space-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M16 1H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14h2V3h12V1zm3 4H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h11c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V7c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H8V7h11v14z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Process Optimization</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Streamline development workflows and implement best practices for efficiency.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-surface-primary p-8 rounded-xl border border-surface-tertiary hover:border-nexus-cyan/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-deep-space-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Security Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Comprehensive security audits and implementation of robust security measures.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-surface-primary p-8 rounded-xl border border-surface-tertiary hover:border-nexus-cyan/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-deep-space-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Performance Optimization</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Identify bottlenecks and optimize applications for maximum performance and scalability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Consulting Process -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface-primary">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center">
          Our Consulting <span class="text-nexus-cyan">Process</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-space-black">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Discovery</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Understand your business goals, challenges, and current technology landscape.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-space-black">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Deep dive into your systems, processes, and identify optimization opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-space-black">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Develop actionable recommendations and implementation roadmaps.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nexus-cyan rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-space-black">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Implementation</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Support execution with hands-on guidance and ongoing optimization.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>